40973,"uid":55731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"試過去譚仔叫雙特辣但個阿姐話無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed412e86ff8fe26288b197316adeba8387b0d6ed","tid":40973,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過去譚仔叫雙特辣但個阿姐話無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過<br />\n我堅持有<br />\n佢就搵個熟d既黎落單"},{"pid":"497fd56aa55bdfc7c17fc140504785d269e66da8","tid":40973,"uid":35653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就好有得食4特<br />\n我試過嗌4特佢話會好杰唔肯整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇試過5特佢肯唔肯整？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇 因為四特已經好難食 苦嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問咩叫四特五特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：小辣廢j"},{"pid":"7bbeea5531569ea35610068c9e726dbf87838c5b","tid":40973,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇試過5特佢肯唔肯整？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇 因為四特已經好難食 苦嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問咩叫四特五特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：小辣廢j</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n四倍特辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/no